dct_title_s: Mapa geologico de la Republica Dominicana 1:250,000: mapa geologico general, hoja de Samana (N-E)
dct_description_sm: Dominican Republic. Direccion General de Mineria. Bundesanstalt fur Geowissenschaften und Rohstoffe (BGR) Instituto Geografico Universitario. Companion text: Mapa geologico de la Repubica Dominicana 1:250,000: texto explicativo / Tabla de las muestras paleontologicas / Hartmut Mollat; Bernhard M. Wagner; Pavel Cepek; Wolfgang Weiss. Hannover: E. Schweizerbart'sche Verlagsbuchhandlung in Kommission. Geologisches Jahrbuch Reihe B, Regionale Geologie Ausland Heft 90. 2004. 100p. 26 fig. 1 table. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Sheet name designation was taken from maps accompanying explanatory text. Another copy of map with source source publication.
dct_publisher_sm: Hannover : Bundesanstalt für Geowissenschaften und Rohstoffe, 1991.
